OL,3,CThe campaign helping foster children
OL,4,Covercome food insecurities
OL,6,FTwo-thirds of foster children in Wales
OL,7,Fhave insecurities around food and meal
OL,8,Ftimes.
OL,10,FA new campaign by Foster Wales hopes
OL,11,Fto give carers the tools they need to
OL,12,Fhelp children overcome worries about
OL,13,Ffood.
OL,15,FBring Something to the Table was
OL,16,Flaunched at Newport Market, along with
OL,17,Fa special cooking demonstration led by
OL,18,FCelebrity Masterchef winner Wynne
OL,19,FEvans.
