OL,6,FFoster Wales carried out a survey
OL,7,Fasking foster carers for their
OL,8,Fexperience at meal times. The results
OL,9,Ffound:
OL,11,FThe feedback helped shape the
OL,12,Fcampaign, which not only hopes to
OL,13,Fsupport foster carers but also recruit
OL,14,Fnew ones around the country.
OL,16,FAlastair Cope, head of Foster Wales
OL,17,Fsaid: "As 22 local authorities working
OL,18,Ftogether across Wales to really spread
OL,19,Fthat message that yes, we need more
OL,20,Ffoster carers.
