OL,3,CThe campaign helping foster children
OL,4,Covercome food insecurities
OL,6,F"But the fact is that everybody can
OL,7,Fbring something to the table. Even if
OL,8,Fpeople don't feel they have the right
OL,9,Fskills or abilities or experience to
OL,10,Flook after a child in care.
OL,12,F"Always come to your local
OL,13,Fauthorities, first port of call, if
OL,14,Fyou're interested in fostering. And
OL,15,Fhave that conversation with you and
OL,16,Fwe'll take you through it every step
OL,17,Fof the way."
