OL,3,CThe campaign helping foster children
OL,4,Covercome food insecurities
OL,6,FJohn Jenkins has six children around
OL,7,Fhis dinner table, four of which are
OL,8,Ffoster children. He said kitchen
OL,9,Fmanagement is crucial: "We have a lot
OL,10,Fof one pot style dishes that were all
OL,11,Fhaving the same meal together.
OL,13,F"If you make spaghetti bolognese one
OL,14,Fday, you have everything you need to
OL,15,Flayer up for a lasagne for the next
OL,16,Fday. Children looking forward to that
OL,17,Fmeal time together, they're having
OL,18,Fthat meal time.
