OL,3,CThe campaign helping foster children
OL,4,Covercome food insecurities
OL,6,F"Feeling like a family. That's the
OL,7,Fmost important thing, it's not what
OL,8,Fthe dish is, what the food is, how you
OL,9,Fcook it or anything like that. It's
OL,10,Fwhat it signifies."
OL,12,FOver the years, Cath Lucas and her
OL,13,Fhusband Neil have fostered 28
OL,14,Fchildren, currently with a baby and
OL,15,Fnine year old in their care.
OL,17,FThey travelled down from Wrexham for
OL,18,Fthe event and to share their tips with
OL,19,Fothers.
