OL,3,CThe campaign helping foster children
OL,4,Covercome food insecurities
OL,6,FCath said: "Some children have lived
OL,7,Fwhere they've had very little food or
OL,8,Fthey've not known where the next meal
OL,9,Fis coming from.
OL,11,F"So we lay the table for them before
OL,12,Fthey go out in the morning and before
OL,13,Fthey go to bed at night, they just
OL,14,Fknow that security is there.
OL,16,F"They're still going to be here at our
OL,17,Fhouse and there's going to be a meal
OL,18,Fprovided for them."
